name: Chicken Biryani
description: A flavorful rice dish made with long-grain basmati rice, tender chicken pieces, aromatic spices, and herbs, cooked to perfection.

name: Chicken Fried Rice
description: A delicious Indo-Chinese dish made with cooked rice, stir-fried with chicken pieces, mixed vegetables, and flavored with soy sauce and spices.

name: Chicken Tandoori
description: Tender chicken marinated in a blend of yogurt and spices, then roasted or grilled to perfection, resulting in a smoky and flavorful dish.

name: Chicken Noodles
description: Stir-fried noodles tossed with tender pieces of chicken, mixed vegetables, and an array of sauces and spices, creating a flavorful and satisfying meal.

name: Chicken 65
description: A spicy and tangy South Indian appetizer made with bite-sized pieces of chicken marinated in a fiery blend of spices and deep-fried until crispy.

name: Pepper Chicken
description: A spicy and flavorful dish made with succulent chicken pieces sautéed with black pepper, onions, curry leaves, and a mix of aromatic spices.

name: Chilli Chicken
description: A popular Indo-Chinese dish made with batter-fried chicken pieces tossed in a spicy and tangy sauce along with bell peppers, onions, and green chilies.

name: Grilled Chicken
description: Tender chicken marinated in a flavorful blend of spices and herbs, then grilled to perfection, resulting in juicy and succulent grilled chicken.

name: Mutton Biryani
description: A fragrant rice dish made with long-grain basmati rice and tender pieces of mutton, cooked with a blend of aromatic spices and herbs, resulting in a rich and flavorful biryani.

name: Mutton Curry
description: Tender pieces of mutton cooked in a spicy and flavorful curry made with onions, tomatoes, yogurt, and a blend of traditional spices, best enjoyed with steamed rice or roti.

name: Mutton Pepper Fry
description: Juicy mutton pieces marinated in a fiery blend of black pepper, ginger, garlic, and other spices, sautéed until tender and crispy, making it a perfect appetizer or side dish.

name: Mutton Rogan Josh
description: A rich and aromatic Kashmiri dish made with tender mutton pieces cooked in a flavorful gravy made with yogurt, onions, tomatoes, and a blend of traditional spices.

name: Fish Manchurian
description: Deep-fried fish balls cooked in a tangy and spicy Manchurian sauce made with soy sauce, garlic, ginger, and green chilies, served as a popular Indo-Chinese appetizer.

name: Prawn Hakka Noodles
description: Stir-fried noodles tossed with juicy prawns, mixed vegetables, and a blend of sauces and spices, creating a delightful and satisfying Indo-Chinese meal.

name: Chilli Fish
description: Crispy fish pieces tossed in a spicy and tangy sauce made with bell peppers, onions, garlic, and green chilies, creating a mouthwatering Indo-Chinese seafood dish.

name: Fish Curry
description: Fresh fish pieces cooked in a flavorful and aromatic curry made with coconut milk, tomatoes, onions, and a blend of traditional spices, best enjoyed with steamed rice.

name: Fish Fry
description: Fresh fish marinated in a blend of spices and herbs, then deep-fried until crispy and golden brown, resulting in a delicious and satisfying seafood dish.
